author: Sadie Gennis, TV GUIDE
title: Will Smith Can Still Get It in New "Fiesta" Music Video
text:
It's been years since Will Smith left his successful rap career behind, but the actor proved he can still get jiggy with it in the new music video for a remix of Bomba Estereo's "Fiesta."
After hearing the Grammy-nominated song, Smith approached the Colombian electronic tropical group about contributing a verse for a remix. And now, the 47-year-old has reteamed with Bomba for a sexy music video in which Smith reminds us that we're all still living in the new Willennium.
